events.title: NYSL Fundraiser
events.content: The season start with the annual NYSL Fundraiser dinner. Anyone interested in attending dinner should contact the organization.

events.title: Season Kick-off: Meet the Teams
events.content: An afternoon of snack so that the players know each other and enjoy before the start of the season.

events.title: Distribution of new uniforms
events.content: The uniforms will be delivered ath the NYSL office during all day.
